What a button will soon appear
Millions of Facebook users have become accustomed to the "Like" button, and now the social network is preparing for its opposite, "Dislike".
Mark Zuckerberg, the company's co-founder and CEO, announced on his Twitter account Tuesday that the button will be available soon, the New York Times blog post reports.
